Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.35,0:00:18.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.23,0:00:20.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦…哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.47,0:00:25.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.90,0:00:33.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.18,0:00:34.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.31,0:00:37.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.66,0:00:42.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给  你的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.08,0:00:48.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.19,0:00:55.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,桐乃桐乃  你爸昨天在参观你工作的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.63,0:00:59.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要拍照的时候被当做可疑人物啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.75,0:01:01.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是吧  讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.06,0:01:04.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要…要你多嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.07,0:01:09.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他一着急  就说「不…不是  这是我女儿」
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.79,0:01:11.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要学我
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.20,0:01:13.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是  爸爸你啊
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.61,0:02:53.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是吧  真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.12,0:02:56.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  真的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.47,0:03:01.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们社长看上了加奈子  要她下次去面试
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.75,0:03:04.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成功了的话  可能会进事务所
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.40,0:03:06.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是偶像的第一步吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.03,0:03:10.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那次的肮脏的工作体验一下也不错
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.40,0:03:14.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思  桐乃等级的我大概很快就追上了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.06,0:03:19.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恭喜你  加奈子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.82,0:03:23.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加奈子肯定会合格的  加油哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.10,0:03:25.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.36,0:03:29.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就我家那个妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.21,0:03:32.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「早上好」啊「Thankyou」啊「你的份」什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.32,0:03:33.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这怎么可能呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.56,0:03:37.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那不是桐乃  是长着桐乃脸的什么东西
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.48,0:03:44.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用在意  桐乃一定也开始想要直率地感谢小京的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.30,0:03:49.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是  总觉得有什么不对呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.36,0:03:56.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呃
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.39,0:03:58.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你「呃」什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.49,0:04:03.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好哥哥  上次承蒙你照顾了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.70,0:04:07.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了呢  桐乃也非常开心
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.80,0:04:08.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.94,0:04:11.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小京的熟人?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.62,0:04:13.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是桐乃的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.82,0:04:16.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,初次见面  我是新垣绫濑
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.08,0:04:19.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好  我是田村麻奈实
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.42,0:04:23.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…  小京的青梅竹马
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.50,0:04:25.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说  绫濑
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.84,0:04:26.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.21,0:04:34.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,并没有特别奇怪的地方啊  和平常一样的桐乃
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.99,0:04:36.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.20,0:04:39.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什么的话我也会发觉的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.44,0:04:40.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们是好朋友啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.36,0:04:42.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.05,0:04:45.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起啊  问了些奇怪的事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.49,0:04:46.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.30,0:04:48.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么我就告辞了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.31,0:04:49.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回见啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.07,0:04:51.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.25,0:04:58.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,确实提出搞活动的是在下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.21,0:05:02.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,桐乃乃氏也很赞同才做准备的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.87,0:05:05.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得并没有特别勉强的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.76,0:05:07.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然是我想多了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.61,0:05:13.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是因为京介氏太在意桐乃乃氏了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.11,0:05:15.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才不是呢  笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.21,0:05:20.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打扰你了  我要挂了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.69,0:05:21.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.77,0:05:22.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Nyoron
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.77,0:05:22.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs18}(注：小凉宫鹤屋前辈的口头必备萌音）
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.20,0:05:31.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.91,0:05:33.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能来下我的房间吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.86,0:05:51.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像变干净了呢  这个房间
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.08,0:05:53.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,稍微整理了一下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.59,0:05:58.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那要说的话是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.14,0:06:01.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是上次说的最后的探讨人生吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.06,0:06:05.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么说也算是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.73,0:06:09.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,算了  说说看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.54,0:06:10.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.28,0:06:13.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.75,0:06:16.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想让你帮我买工口游戏
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.69,0:06:19.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这算啥
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.14,0:06:22.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.51,0:06:26.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「我绝对没有偷哥哥的短裤哦」
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.82,0:06:29.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有这个「3D定制妹妹」
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.81,0:06:31.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是「哥裤」和「定制妹」
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.65,0:06:33.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是什么略称
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.33,0:06:36.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这两部我想让你深夜排队帮我买
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.70,0:06:40.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是最后的探讨人生吗  真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.13,0:06:41.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.17,0:06:43.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么要拜托我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.08,0:06:47.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然是因为这种事哪怕快一秒做也是好的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.04,0:06:51.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,按照预定傍晚睡上一觉  等你把游戏买回来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.86,0:06:54.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,准备一直玩到早上  通完一条线
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.37,0:06:56.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这家伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.31,0:06:58.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要做到这种地步吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.23,0:07:01.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要啊  当然要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.56,0:07:04.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是啊  那间店不是在秋叶原吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.58,0:07:08.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算晚上12点去买回到家也要过1点了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.74,0:07:10.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是被老爸发现…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.13,0:07:12.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这边我会想办法的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.59,0:07:15.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸他们的动向我会用电话联系你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.38,0:07:19.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无论如何我都想快点玩到
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.35,0:07:22.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好不好  这是最后了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.98,0:07:26.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.43,0:07:32.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道啦  我去买就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.94,0:07:35.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的？  太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.29,0:07:41.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉赤城  今晚就当我住在你家行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.02,0:07:42.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦  好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.57,0:07:46.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和田村好好玩哦  拜
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.73,0:07:50.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他好像误会了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.30,0:07:54.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好冷啊喂
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.78,0:08:06.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这些全部都是桐乃的同类啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.25,0:08:12.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,参加深夜发售的客人  请在这里排队
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.20,0:08:26.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,骑着那个到这里来的么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.56,0:08:29.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个  最末尾是这里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.05,0:08:31.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.96,0:08:35.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赤…赤城？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.74,0:08:37.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高坂…吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.74,0:08:44.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是拜托你就当今晚我住在你家的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.71,0:08:46.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么你会来买工口游戏啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.74,0:08:49.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里面有很深的原因…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.66,0:08:53.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说  我还以为你和田村去了什么地方呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.60,0:08:55.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么你会来买工口游戏啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.66,0:08:58.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里面有很深的原因…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.37,0:09:03.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来彼此都有苦衷啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.09,0:09:08.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就当我们根本没有在这里见过吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.16,0:09:15.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我和你都没有去秋叶原的深夜发售
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.33,0:09:16.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有排队
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.64,0:09:19.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然没有买什么工口游戏
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.28,0:09:26.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,友情是不求回报的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.51,0:09:31.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,预定了「搞基部」的客人  请到这里排队
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.57,0:09:32.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.86,0:09:42.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你你…那个就是所谓的纯搞基游戏？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.50,0:09:46.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高坂  你误会大了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.82,0:09:48.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听我说  看着我的眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.90,0:09:50.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要靠近我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.56,0:09:51.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我才不是基
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.23,0:09:54.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,确实那是纯搞基游戏
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.54,0:09:57.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是那我妹妹拜托我来买的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.02,0:10:00.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你妹不还是初中生吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.98,0:10:05.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪个世界会有让哥哥去买工口游戏的初中生妹妹…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.86,0:10:09.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许有呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.70,0:10:12.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么认同了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.69,0:10:19.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个世界上有太多无法用常识来解释的事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.15,0:10:21.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怀疑你真抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.99,0:10:24.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  你能理解就好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.83,0:10:27.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你妹妹玩基情游戏吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.72,0:10:30.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我家妹妹就是所谓的腐女子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.05,0:10:34.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是妇人的妇  而是腐臭的腐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.34,0:10:39.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,基本上幻想男人间的恋爱或亲密关系
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.36,0:10:41.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,偷偷地享受
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.31,0:10:45.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总之就是喜欢基啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.41,0:10:47.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最喜欢了  热爱着啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.78,0:10:55.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么要拍手呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.89,0:10:58.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁知道  我已经明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.23,0:11:00.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别管我了去那边的队伍吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.05,0:11:02.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  回见
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.34,0:11:08.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家久等了  开始发售了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.08,0:11:12.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请听从工作人员的引导购买商品
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.24,0:11:16.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么从前面的人开始每次十人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.28,0:11:17.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请给我「短裤」
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.59,0:11:19.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也要「哥哥的短裤」
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.92,0:11:22.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是收银台
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.07,0:11:27.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最后一趟电车还赶得上吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.53,0:11:43.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,买到了？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.63,0:11:45.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,告诉我你脑袋的尺寸
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.89,0:11:51.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之前不是说过吗  要给你做一个猫耳
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.69,0:11:55.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快告诉我你那又大又圆的脑袋的尺寸
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.55,0:11:59.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是你啊  这种事用邮件问不就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.46,0:12:02.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今晚服务器维护上不了线
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.32,0:12:04.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以打算录在电话留言里的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.20,0:12:07.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然明天也可以
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.42,0:12:10.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但莫名地想要今晚问你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.74,0:12:12.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还醒着太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.74,0:12:15.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说  你把我错当谁了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.31,0:12:27.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太过分了  也真亏哥哥会容忍你的旁若无人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.69,0:12:31.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,烦死了  话说你能不能不要那么叫他
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.78,0:12:32.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.76,0:12:34.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说实话真恶心
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.37,0:12:38.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被你这么一叫他就一副扭捏的样子真是恶心
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.25,0:12:40.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我倒没看出来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.72,0:12:43.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过没关系  到时称呼就会改变的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.83,0:12:44.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.52,0:13:01.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在哪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.45,0:13:02.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,窗户打开
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.70,0:13:31.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给  这个
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.62,0:13:36.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.54,0:13:38.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.49,0:13:42.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我去睡了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.89,0:13:45.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早上得出去一次才行呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.71,0:13:47.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你上学也别迟到了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.07,0:13:49.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等…等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.53,0:13:53.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一起玩吗  很久没一起玩了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.47,0:13:57.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂…别靠太近了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.22,0:14:00.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没办法呀  不这样我就看不到画面了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.87,0:14:04.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,安装完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.03,0:14:08.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「我才没有偷哥哥的内裤哦」
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.97,0:14:11.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次虽然女主角只有一个
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.96,0:14:14.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是相对却有很多路线
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.44,0:14:18.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每次通关都会增加选项  结局也会改变
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.43,0:14:20.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过这也是经常有的形式
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.59,0:14:23.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有潜入一样的迷你游戏
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.69,0:14:26.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在那里得到的道具可以用来立flag
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.56,0:14:35.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是什么结局  也太悲伤了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.30,0:14:39.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗  他们又不是生离死别
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.72,0:14:41.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打打电话不就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.17,0:14:42.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笨蛋  真是笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.84,0:14:44.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你什么都不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.24,0:14:46.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想见的时候见不到很寂寞吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.53,0:14:48.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你自己换位思考一下试试啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.37,0:14:51.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧  那倒也是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.16,0:14:55.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么想的话的确是个寂寞的结局
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.30,0:14:56.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.14,0:14:59.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白就好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.73,0:15:02.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得回收一下分歧路线
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.10,0:15:08.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,达成一个结局了  已经可以了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.25,0:15:10.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等…等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.53,0:15:12.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干嘛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.95,0:15:15.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,探讨人生
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.96,0:15:18.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不是说那是最后的探讨人生
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.97,0:15:20.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我才去买工口游戏的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.47,0:15:23.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是还没有结束
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.05,0:15:28.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有什么  说来听听
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.38,0:15:40.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是不是多了？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.62,0:15:43.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  从那以后都过了9个月了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.12,0:15:46.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还记得那时的事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.60,0:15:48.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,记得吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.21,0:15:54.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实那个时候呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.07,0:15:58.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有因为害羞没让你看的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.53,0:16:03.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也有好好保密  也没有看不起我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.76,0:16:05.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还帮了我那么多
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.91,0:16:07.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.95,0:16:11.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是比动画和工口游戏更糟糕的东西吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.83,0:16:16.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然很害羞  还是让你看看
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.25,0:16:17.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我才不想看
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.50,0:16:35.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比想象的要普通嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.60,0:16:38.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我妹妹的东西不可能这么普通
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.48,0:16:41.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,特别是那个很糟糕  相册很糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.47,0:16:43.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,根本不知道那里面放了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.99,0:16:46.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个啊  这本相册啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.92,0:16:49.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要看吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.58,0:16:53.52,SPEC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(550,137)\fad(0,600)} 不看
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.58,0:16:53.52,SPEC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(55,137)\fad(0,600)} 看
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.96,0:16:55.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了  给我看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.01,0:16:57.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要看啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.17,0:17:00.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都到这个地步  我做好觉悟了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.66,0:17:04.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,倒是蒙在鼓里才更让人精神上不爽
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.07,0:17:06.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拿来吧  给我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.53,0:17:10.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然还是算了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.80,0:17:13.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,提出来的可是你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.61,0:17:15.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吵死了  我改变主意了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.00,0:17:17.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没你事了  快回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.09,0:17:18.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那算什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.30,0:17:22.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,差遣别人一整晚  怎么这个态度
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.98,0:17:24.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.64,0:17:35.52,SPEC2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(40,250)\fad(0,200)}东京/成田\N↓\N洛杉矶
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.09,0:17:41.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要去美国吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.41,0:17:45.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.41,0:17:46.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊不  今天？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.24,0:17:48.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和你没关系吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.81,0:17:50.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.59,0:17:52.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你去干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.45,0:17:54.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么时候回来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.10,0:18:00.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在那边接受田径训练
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.65,0:18:02.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在升高中前不会回来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.13,0:18:06.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏天合宿的时候  被那边的教练看上了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.37,0:18:09.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得这是次不错的机会就接受了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.65,0:18:11.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你…为什么突然…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.80,0:18:12.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是突然
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.40,0:18:17.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这半年来都在通过工作和小说的钱筹备费用
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.84,0:18:19.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也和父亲和母亲说过了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.55,0:18:22.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就剩下天亮去机场了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.09,0:18:26.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么就瞒着我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.83,0:18:32.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没必要说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.79,0:18:37.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算我不在了  和你有关系吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.28,0:18:38.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…  喂
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.80,0:18:39.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兄妹…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.47,0:18:42.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不会现在说叫我不要去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.59,0:18:44.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,准备也全部做好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.85,0:18:47.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也觉得我烦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.65,0:18:50.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也觉得你很烦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.49,0:18:56.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,的确如你所说
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.08,0:18:58.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,田径  美国
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.21,0:19:00.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很不错的机会嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.46,0:19:03.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完全没有阻止你的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.22,0:19:07.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去吧  你去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.14,0:19:09.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这事和我没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.30,0:19:13.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用你说我也会去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.25,0:19:14.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.43,0:19:15.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会去的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.23,0:19:16.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.49,0:19:18.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在就去  立刻就去  给我去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.25,0:19:20.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这家伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.04,0:19:25.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.66,0:19:26.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.38,0:19:28.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手啊  笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.44,0:19:28.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老爸会…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.01,0:19:29.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.53,0:19:36.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去死  去死  去死
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.50,0:19:39.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,（留住法奈）
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.60,0:19:42.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.00,0:19:44.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要我怎么做啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.05,0:19:48.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「说声『不要走』呀  哥哥」
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.84,0:19:55.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「哥哥要留住我的话  我哪里都不去了」
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.09,0:20:03.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「梦想在哪里都能实现  但哥哥只在这里」
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.39,0:20:06.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「谢谢你  哥哥」
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.51,0:20:09.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「今后也要一直在一起哦」
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.22,0:20:15.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.63,0:20:18.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就清静了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.20,0:21:09.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你什么时候回来的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.68,0:21:10.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.04,0:21:11.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.55,0:21:25.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦  你回来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.79,0:21:28.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么办  饭还够吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.66,0:21:31.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,桐乃呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.73,0:21:33.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,烦人  让开啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.53,0:21:42.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好  爸爸妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.34,0:21:43.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.56,0:21:44.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.69,0:21:46.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,飞机是几点来着？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.31,0:21:48.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早饭吃了再走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.79,0:21:52.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经说了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.66,0:21:55.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,关于那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.12,0:21:58.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不去美国了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.23,0:22:00.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.25,0:22:04.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不去了  你…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.62,0:22:06.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.56,0:22:08.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天我会去各处道歉的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.70,0:22:10.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晚上我会说明的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.45,0:22:12.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.07,0:22:13.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是…是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.97,0:22:16.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过我到是不介意
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.51,0:22:18.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.64,0:22:22.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美国又远  你也还只是中学生呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.54,0:22:33.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你老是说去吧去吧的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.17,0:22:37.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,突然觉得很不爽  扫兴了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.22,0:22:39.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然和你没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.03,0:22:40.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.70,0:22:44.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过英语也还需要学习一下
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.87,0:22:46.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有梅露露的电影
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.74,0:22:49.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和绫濑她们分开也会寂寞的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.77,0:22:52.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,进了高中再编入也比较方便
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.59,0:22:55.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且钱也能适当返还一些
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.42,0:23:00.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸妈妈…那些家伙也会寂寞的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.70,0:23:02.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那边要买工口游戏…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.37,0:23:08.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚开始就干嘛笑嘻嘻
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.64,0:23:09.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,超恶心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.60,0:23:12.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才没有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.80,0:23:14.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哼  笨～蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.73,0:23:25.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小京早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.44,0:23:29.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天似乎心情很好嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.59,0:23:30.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.68,0:23:33.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在想什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.34,0:23:35.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没什么大不了的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.35,0:23:42.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是  我的妹妹
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.68,0:25:02.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.54,0:25:26.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.77,0:25:28.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.61,0:25:31.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有些事需要…
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.19,0:25:36.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,探讨人生
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.45,0:25:40.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喔！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:13.38,0:27:13.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下回
Dialogue: 0,0:27:14.05,0:27:17.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我妹妹的探讨人生不可能就这么结束了
